{"tid":1564839,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"問數","createTime":"2019-09-13T02:23:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T02:52:45.000Z","uid":104440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"af8acd220fdf0813ac6922c833c91b115c3d8da4","tid":1564839,"uid":104440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:23:33.000Z","msg":"There is an unknown number. When it is divided by 3, 5 and 7, it will give 2, 3 and 2 as a remainder respectively. What is the general form of the possible value?<br />\n<br />\n淨係識得 做左 除3同除7先<br />\nN=3a+2=7b+2<br />\nN=21c+2<br />\n<br />\n咁 N=21c+2=5d+3<br />\n唔識拆<br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n另外係咪有得一次過計, 唔駛分2個step 方法"},{"pid":"9b65729f468f29b71a280982f2048d2033aa6789","tid":1564839,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:24:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"72295e58a2e906e2dd5d2635560516c0b7e41f8b","tid":1564839,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:24:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f162cb38d89be871ca7474f05c44a580d7ae5df","tid":1564839,"uid":79403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T02:31:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://nrich.maths.org/5466\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.